text: Kauhajoki is a town in Southern Ostrobothnia, Finland. As of 28 February 2023, 12,723 people lived there. Neighbouring municipalities are Isojoki, Kankaanpää, Karijoki, Karvia, Kurikka and Teuva. == Other websites == * Town of Kauhajoki – Official website Category:Municipalities of South Ostrobothnia Category:Towns in Finland
